m\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fnchs%2Fnvss%2Fvsrr%2Fcovid_weekly%2Findex.htm&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5r4lFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=fb575515\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cdc.gov/nchs/nvss/vsrr/covid_weekly/index.htm</a><br />\n<br />\nFor 6% of the deaths, COVID-19 was the only cause mentioned.<br />\n<br />\n樓豬應該討論嘅唔係廢炎殺傷力<br />\n而係廢炎引起併發症而瓜嘅人計唔計廢炎殺<br />\n比如話同樣嘅長期病 中感冒係咪都瓜呢<br />\n好多人本身都cancer 末期 加多個感冒都瓜鳩硬 咁都計廢炎殺<br />\n呢樣你真係自己思考下再講啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T05:40:54.000Z","msg":"你睇清楚個解釋先<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/amp/idUSKBN25U2IO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Famp%2FidUSKBN25U2IO&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5r4lFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=0d218839\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Famp%2FidUSKBN25U2IO&h=01c956cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/amp/idUSKBN25U2IO</a><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;The claim that the CDC &ldquo;admitted that only 6% of&hellip; (COVID-19-related) deaths recorded actually died from Covid&rdquo; is false, because the remaining 94% of cases were instances of comorbidity (the existence of two or more conditions or illnesses in a patient). This does not exclude COVID-19, but combines it with other illnesses, often triggered by the new coronavirus itself.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Dr. Maja Artandi ( here ), medical director of the Stanford CROWN Clinic for COVID-19 patients ( here ), told Reuters via email that the CDC&rsquo;s numbers &ldquo;are really not a big surprise,&rdquo; as &ldquo;patients who have a comorbidity such as diabetes, hypertension or obesity have a higher risk of getting seriously ill and dying from COVID-19.&rdquo; The numbers are also consistent with the fact that the novel coronavirus &ldquo;can cause severe damage to the organs in the body such as the lungs, which then leads to respiratory failure and death.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nKey to understanding the issues in these posts is that, &ldquo;If they had not gotten the infection,&rdquo; Dr. Artandi said, &ldquo;they would still be alive.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"e18e76b3f28876c988663419a43e5cfe240d2c90","tid":2295823,"uid":87571,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0025145bb628087b03253e036385f5fe35038cb2","tid":2295823,"uid":78016,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ed7ff5cf6fcd0f61c512d479b0ec4954ed10ec56","tid":2295823,"uid":87571,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1ec6d376be8592bfdc4cafa49d56d18cb315acb","tid":2295823,"uid":33125,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T05:02:30.000Z","msg":"好多唔關事既都計落covid到wor..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T05:08:28.000Z","msg":"唔好聽人鳩吹啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T05:18:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8750139/Scientists-claim-UK-covid-19-victims-July-August-died-causes.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-8750139%2FScientists-claim-UK-covid-19-victims-July-August-died-causes.html&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5r4lFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=a5cb2b01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8750139/Scientists-claim-UK-covid-19-victims-July-August-died-causes.html</a><br />\n<br />\n撞車死都計廢炎<br />\n新聞報左 哈佛又認證<br />\n係咪鳩吹呀 屌你老母<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T05:49:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/volumes/69/wr/mm6942e2.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fmmwr%2Fvolumes%2F69%2Fwr%2Fmm6942e2.htm&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5r4lFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=c7c04db3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.c